{"id":237103,"type":1,"name":"ぱらのま","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/8e/ad/237103_Vo9R3.jpg","summary":"与「残念的大姐姐」一同将精力挥霍在无尽的铁路旅行上。「乘坐铁路」「铁路摄影」等等、类似喜爱铁路的方式还很多，而她的方式则是「铁路旅行」。\r\n\r\n日本全国津々浦々を鉄道で移動する女性の旅を描いたマンガ。駅弁を食べるだけのために特急のかいじに乗ったり、大阪名古屋方面から東京への帰りに伊豆に寄り道したりと、思いのままのんびりと旅をする“鉄子”の姿が描かれている。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>全景之旅</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/6679\">kashmir</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/588\">白泉社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8750\">楽園 Le Paradis</a>、楽園web増刊</li><li><span>开始: </span>2015-02-28(楽園第17号) / 2015-04-04(楽園2015年春のweb増刊)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"doing":3,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":6679,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1a/7d/6679_prsn_lVtV9.jpg","name":"kashmir","desc":"作者"},{"id":588,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/2a/588_prsn_0Fa4a.jpg","name":"白泉社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8750,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7c/07/8750_prsn_Se9uE.jpg","name":"乐园 Le Paradis","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":123982,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3d/4c/123982_f4fHN.jpg","title":"てるみな","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123982"}],"comic":[{"id":217289,"name":"ぱらのま 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f9/da/217289_jp.jpg"},{"id":262355,"name":"ぱらのま 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/0b/af/262355_e4tNd.jpg"},{"id":305575,"name":"ぱらのま 3","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1f/53/305575_7zv34.jpg"},{"id":335927,"name":"ぱらのま 4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d6/eb/335927_63JE5.jpg"}]}